{"tid":2260817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習權統治｜宗教寺廟頻被查唯毛澤東廟任開 廟祝：習近平走毛的路","createTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"272bc53de0bf30d105533cb54dc59d63aa05af30","tid":2260817,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"今日為國際宗教自由日，長期關注中國宗教自由及人權狀況的網媒《寒冬》（Bitter Winter）報道，疫情期間，內地關閉廟宇，禁止民眾拜祭，惟擺放中共已故領導人毛澤東人像的廟宇，卻如獲「免死金牌」，民眾可以自出自入。「疫情封鎖時期除了這座廟別處廟都關門了，來這裏拜毛澤東的人一直沒有間斷，政府也沒來限制、關停這座廟。」河南南陽市新野縣一名村民說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201028/A4RPVFNCHRFOHGSUQYHQCCERTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201028%2FA4RPVFNCHRFOHGSUQYHQCCERTQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDJvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=294dbc18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201028%2FA4RPVFNCHRFOHGSUQYHQCCERTQ%2F&h=15d8d557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201028/A4RPVFNCHRFOHGSUQYHQCCERTQ/</a>"}]}